==Philippines==
TV5 will broadcast the entirety of Season 1 of the anime, beginning January 9, 2017. It will be shown on Mondays, Tuesdays and Thursdays, at 5:15 PM, GMT+8. It will be dubbed in Tagalog, the main Filipino dialect.

Due to being aired in free TV, each episode is split into parts, and certain risque scenes omitted or blurred in compliance with the country's broadcast regulation body, [[wikipedia:MTRCB|MTRCB]]. The show is rated PG.

